OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 13 JUN
OL,4,CBROADCAST BUILDINGS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1972FHRH The Duke of Kent officially
OL,7,Fopens Kent House. The building is the
OL,8,Fnew home of London Weekend Television's
OL,9,FLondon Studios. The Duke and Duchess of
OL,10,FKent, attend a gala evening of music
OL,11,Fand wit at the Queen Elizabeth Hall.
OL,12,
OL,13,CG1991FThe Late Show is the final live
OL,14,Fprogramme broadcast from BBC Lime
OL,15,FGrove. The final portion of the
OL,16,Fprogramme - with a symbolic unplugging
OL,17,Fof a camera power cord in Studio D by
OL,18,FCliff Michelmore - was pre-recorded.
